OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,FWorkplaces are being warned they could
OL,7,Fface action from the equalities
OL,8,Fregulator if they fail to take
OL,9,Freasonable steps to prevent sexual
OL,10,Fharassment under a new law coming into
OL,11,Fforce next month.
OL,13,FThe legislation for England, Scotland
OL,14,Fand Wales introduces a preventative
OL,15,Fduty on employers to stop workplace
OL,16,Fharassment, instead of relying on
OL,17,Femployees to report incidents.
