OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,FThe Worker Protection (Amendment of
OL,7,FEquality Act 2010) Act, due to come in
OL,8,Ffrom October 26, is aimed at improving
OL,9,Fworkplace cultures and preventing
OL,10,Fsexual harassment.
OL,12,FPreviously there was no pro-active
OL,13,Flegal obligation on employers to take
OL,14,Fsteps to prevent sexual harassment at
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,FThe new obligation comes in the wake
OL,18,Fof what the Fawcett Society has
OL,19,Fpreviously described as a "slew of
OL,20,Frecent high-profile cases (which)
OL,21,Fshows it is rife in our workplaces".
