OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,7,FCommission (EHRC) has published new
OL,8,Fguidance ahead of the legislation
OL,9,Fcoming into force, saying this will
OL,10,Fhelp employers understand their
OL,11,Fobligations.
OL,13,FThe act includes the ability for
OL,14,Fcompensation in sexual harassment
OL,15,Fclaims to be increased by up to a
OL,16,Fquarter if an employment tribunal
OL,17,Ffinds a worker has been sexually
OL,18,Fharassed and that the employer's
OL,19,Fpreventative duty has not been met.
