OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,FProtections in the legislation were
OL,7,Fwatered down as it made its way
OL,8,Fthrough Parliament, with Conservative
OL,9,Fpeers in the Lords having raised
OL,10,Fconcerns about free speech and
OL,11,Femployers becoming at risk of costly
OL,12,Flawsuits.
OL,14,FAs a result of a compromise, plans to
OL,15,Fmake employers liable for harassment
OL,16,Fof their employees by third parties
OL,17,Fwere struck out of the legislation.
