OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,FMeasures in the bill insisting
OL,7,Femployers take every reasonable step
OL,8,Fto prevent sexual harassment were also
OL,9,Fwatered down.
OL,11,FEHRC chairwoman Baroness Kishwer
OL,12,FFalkner said: "Sexual harassment
OL,13,Fcontinues to be widespread and often
OL,14,Funder-reported. Everyone has a right
OL,15,Fto feel safe and supported at work.
OL,17,F"The new preventative duty coming into
OL,18,Fforce on October 26 aims to improve
OL,19,Fworkplace cultures by requiring
OL,20,Femployers to proactively protect their
OL,21,Fworkers from sexual harassment.
