OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,F"Employers will need to take
OL,7,Freasonable steps to safeguard their
OL,8,Fworkers. We have updated our guidance
OL,9,Fto ensure they understand their
OL,10,Fobligations and the kinds of steps
OL,11,Fthey can take.
OL,13,F"We will be monitoring compliance with
OL,14,Fthe new duty and will not hesitate to
OL,15,Ftake enforcement action where
OL,16,Fnecessary."
