OL,3,CEmployers warned to protect workers
OL,4,Cfrom sexual harassment ahead of new law
OL,6,F"This law is a big step forward and
OL,7,Fit's testament to the power of Fawcett
OL,8,Fand our members and allies working
OL,9,Ftogether to bring about changes that
OL,10,Fmakes workplaces work for women.
OL,12,F"We will continue to campaign to
OL,13,Fstrengthen the law, and enforcement,
OL,14,Funtil working cultures that allow
OL,15,Fsexual harassment to thrive are
OL,16,Fconsigned to the history books."
